  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif\">At 9th level, you have developed a fail safe for your power charges and can ensure their efficiency. When you roll your charge potency dice, you can reroll a number of dice equal to your Intelligence modifier. If you do so, you must use the new rolls and you can't use this feature again until you finish a short or long rest.</span></p><h4><span style=\"font-family:rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif\">You can use this feature twice between rests starting at 13th level and three times between rests starting at 18th level.</span></h4>",
